author: Reuters
title: BRIEF-DHC software, partner plan to set up unit in Hainan province
text:
Sept 9 DHC Software Co Ltd
* Says it and partner plan to set up a unit in Hainan province with registered capital of 100 million yuan ($15.68 million)
